{"tid":2338212,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門人與市區人日常作息對比","createTime":"2020-12-24T01:12:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T16:51:21.000Z","uid":78016,"like":51,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"93bdef54569b48a7618544d0bee3364dab852eff","tid":2338212,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T01:12:01.000Z","msg":"早上五點九 天未光<br />\n屯門人已經起床梳洗<br />\n市區人仲係被入面享受充足睡眠<br />\n<br />\n早上六點 太陽伯伯出來<br />\n屯門人梳洗好準備出門口 (驚窒車)<br />\n市區人仍在被窩裏與周公捉棋<br />\n<br />\n早上六點半 晨曦照射著在巴士的屯門人<br />\n屯門人已經係巴士 諗緊屯門今日塞唔塞<br />\n市區人禁熄鬧鐘繼續懶床<br />\n<br />\n早上七點 早上陽光好撚刺眼<br />\n屯門人有驚無險過左屯公 終於可以鬆一口氣<br />\n市區人懶床完終於起身<br />\n<br />\n好撚眼訓呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d2372987fee9624d4326569cccb3cab8bd54e5","tid":2338212,"uid":196924,"like":68,"dislike":1,"score":67,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T01:24:50.000Z","msg":"最笨實唔係住屯門，而係住屯門搵份觀塘工"},{"pid":"3a87974165cc7b83f57e9c6e1967128800a3b8a7","tid":2338212,"uid":154255,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T01:31:43.000Z","msg":"有冇少少自己嘅創意啊？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fc93f8d8102f1cd6c61b660f5c9220f4cc7e7e8","tid":2338212,"uid":357591,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T01:51:36.000Z","msg":"點解呢個題目會開係感情台？"},{"pid":"2d78c16e5dc7eb3ecfa77808904f3adb4fa2e5a8","tid":2338212,"uid":165665,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e7d2372987fee9624d4326569cccb3cab8bd54e5","tid":2338212,"uid":196924,"like":68,"dislike":1,"score":67,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T01:24:50.000Z","msg":"最笨實唔係住屯門，而係住屯門搵份觀塘工"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T02:03:24.000Z","msg":"我屯門返觀塘都係7:00先醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f7cc49fcfcb03563d34ef79f3c6fd420e1b60f","tid":2338212,"uid":191926,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T02:05:48.000Z","msg":"不容外區勢力說三道四 干預屯門內政"},{"pid":"f62cd